{"tid":326324,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(巴絲打請入)疑似爆肺, 好痛, 點算好?","createTime":"2017-07-18T01:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T10:46:27.000Z","uid":108922,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c52bcd4ee8094c5fcd284e1e616ebc31dd406f6c","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:51:33.000Z","msg":"我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfcce9746ea0feda934b74d0484ecf261656d8c","tid":326324,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9395c763b11cdf3537014af8ac53f4246034c0c2","tid":326324,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇急症啦屌"},{"pid":"b94cdaa23fd5f0a6d57a9a782a8550fba24a3553","tid":326324,"uid":60916,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:54:04.000Z","msg":"爆肺我諗你1個禮拜已經死左<br />\n好大機會係胸口肌肉拉傷"},{"pid":"c874af6408f31f357840bcda5f2b588e866b2385","tid":326324,"uid":7915,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"為公司捐軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be294568f273a3a9af3246defcf77d677f100f16","tid":326324,"uid":55113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"應該係睇呼吸系統科"},{"pid":"693b311ec0067915f0a1e927cae6f9efce3ce075","tid":326324,"uid":1550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"奴隸"},{"pid":"0707d154edd6157df4c2ddfd77506b531f265510","tid":326324,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆肺我諗你1個禮拜已經死左<br />\n好大機會係胸口肌肉拉傷</blockquote><br />\n爆肺唔一定會死架巴打 <br />\n利伸：爆過兩次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e8501d07a1a34d376b4f619febc0a2200f8886","tid":326324,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:58:39.000Z","msg":"btw 回樓主可以睇急症"},{"pid":"007e158b77a5d6673193283bf385c0fe17a97729","tid":326324,"uid":71568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年"},{"pid":"169c0ea4f9a331741677559eeaa8478388ee8dd1","tid":326324,"uid":123633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"睇急症 同姑娘講你懷疑爆肺<br />\n你再拖就唔止要抖七八日，命都無<br />\n<br />\n利申 爆過肺"},{"pid":"265790de00f650bbc7246b39427b3097df837495","tid":326324,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爆肺可以3年唔理都無事?"},{"pid":"806c88f085ea7b3c7b4724d6f3577978772f5c5c","tid":326324,"uid":34921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:05:02.000Z","msg":"急症啦on9<br />\n爆肺拖得耐會死人<br />\n你講果個症狀都似係<br />\n利申 : 爆過"},{"pid":"314efdf4b5a8133c8822e5274b0e7d75c186922a","tid":326324,"uid":38668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"咪鳩, 隱隱疼就去急症照"},{"pid":"82931b4a3198e7c2e0ff8de14a5738c03f781eaa","tid":326324,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爆肺可以3年唔理都無事?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身唔想講 驚點錯人<br />\n爆肺可以自己收復既<br />\n一般好彩既話小型爆肺係可以自己收復<br />\n但係你唔知佢會唔會惡化 惡化左就大撚鑊<br />\n而我當年係爆到入邊流曬血都自己好得番我諗就睇體質<br />\n但係因為拖太耐所以後黎要切左少少左肺"},{"pid":"857be8b4e31598990e51e9e840e1b48fcc02e0d1","tid":326324,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"On9重上o黎問"},{"pid":"3fa0edb8540ff5b80d5d3cbb848c825c32c546c5","tid":326324,"uid":36078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:10:04.000Z","msg":"入醫院咪諗啦，可大可小呀"},{"pid":"f80d20090f6fbb8d89b3ebb34704cbf1dd0c38da","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇急症 同姑娘講你懷疑爆肺<br />\n你再拖就唔止要抖七八日，命都無<br />\n<br />\n利申 爆過肺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇插喉做手術?係咪好痛?"},{"pid":"48e0c1064f7b4674b4774b41c358504a6f24bb08","tid":326324,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"去私家照左X光先啦，係爆先去急症室。<br />\n利申 爆左成個星期先入院。"},{"pid":"ced73f7ee33b3816aa30a3fa00dc9b4c35a903cd","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直情係吸得好微弱, 要大力索<br />\n<br />\n你3年都好勁吓"},{"pid":"b7960136ee39ad22128a93677aee0b0c3d6fa2a2","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去私家照左X光先啦，係爆先去急症室。<br />\n利申 爆左成個星期先入院。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胸肺科? 耳鼻喉係咪冇用?"},{"pid":"5fabbff427b3d9abb53f65113620f5376dc4d1e2","tid":326324,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇急症 同姑娘講你懷疑爆肺<br />\n你再拖就唔止要抖七八日，命都無<br />\n<br />\n利申 爆過肺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇插喉做手術?係咪好痛?</blockquote><br />\n根據個人經驗<br />\n輕微既你同意之後會即場係急症室做插喉<br />\n麻醉完就黎料，feel到痛就同醫生講<br />\n好快做完之後等上房<br />\nbtw 巴打去急症未"},{"pid":"d18d03031d69b138d5b035acb229bc14c978300e","tid":326324,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直情係吸得好微弱, 要大力索<br />\n<br />\n你3年都好勁吓</blockquote><br />\n係咪好似有野頂住吸唔到氣咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2403f1832b9b8b295327c79b38c289ca392aad1c","tid":326324,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09480a50cd56dc1abb4afcffd68d6c7ac62edf56","tid":326324,"uid":120095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚既睇急症，先唔講連登啲人專唔專業，大佬啊隔住個mon幫你睇實斷到症啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：爆過6次"},{"pid":"c360d5b3904e7f8133b579fad15eaaa6e66227c0","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇急症 同姑娘講你懷疑爆肺<br />\n你再拖就唔止要抖七八日，命都無<br />\n<br />\n利申 爆過肺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇插喉做手術?係咪好痛?</blockquote><br />\n根據個人經驗<br />\n輕微既你同意之後會即場係急症室做插喉<br />\n麻醉完就黎料，feel到痛就同醫生講<br />\n好快做完之後等上房<br />\nbtw 巴打去急症未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未, 仲喺office 做奴隸<br />\nbtw 我係絲打"},{"pid":"81e3f2d33f0ed7187ec1918e30e8c03640db4cf4","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直情係吸得好微弱, 要大力索<br />\n<br />\n你3年都好勁吓</blockquote><br />\n係咪好似有野頂住吸唔到氣咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ae8c9f9e701c56f1ffa773799fe25618eb2cef","tid":326324,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爆肺可以3年唔理都無事?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身唔想講 驚點錯人<br />\n爆肺可以自己收復既<br />\n一般好彩既話小型爆肺係可以自己收復<br />\n但係你唔知佢會唔會惡化 惡化左就大撚鑊<br />\n而我當年係爆到入邊流曬血都自己好得番我諗就睇體質<br />\n但係因為拖太耐所以後黎要切左少少左肺</blockquote><br />\n爆個一次小型, 第一晚一訓低係好痛, 痛到訓唔到, 個肺有卜, 卜, 卜漏氣感覺<br />\n第2日睇急症x ray 見到縮左3cm到, 醫生話好輕微, 休息幾日冇入院就好返<br />\n<br />\n如果訓低有卜, 卜, 卜漏氣感覺, 都幾肯定爆左"},{"pid":"3da28728a6a69b84e2d4e81c963629d9ebc66b67","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚既睇急症，先唔講連登啲人專唔專業，大佬啊隔住個mon幫你睇實斷到症啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：爆過6次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明<br />\n我都係問吓啫, 做決定嗰個係我嚟<br />\n只不過唔想睇錯科, 嘥時間嘥錢啫"},{"pid":"95bcfe65987c15e397c3b39bc499f2ed53b5cc76","tid":326324,"uid":63641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"吸大淡氣，hold 住，二邊有無唔平衡？"},{"pid":"d68b78494b739e0bb8878b6f0720c92c58c72b7a","tid":326324,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落好似爆肺<br />\n巴打有冇呼吸愈來愈短/短左 <br />\n有唔洗諗 直去急症啦屌<br />\n拖得太嚴重有機會要切左一邊佢最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年就係以為打波拉傷忍撚左3年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直情係吸得好微弱, 要大力索<br />\n<br />\n你3年都好勁吓</blockquote><br />\n係咪好似有野頂住吸唔到氣咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都似係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437a8808ee26f416f7a1d482c6fc7e153a07cda7","tid":326324,"uid":120095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚既睇急症，先唔講連登啲人專唔專業，大佬啊隔住個mon幫你睇實斷到症啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：爆過6次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明<br />\n我都係問吓啫, 做決定嗰個係我嚟<br />\n只不過唔想睇錯科, 嘥時間嘥錢啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放心，斷症方法一定係照x ray，得x ray可以睇到，樓上講既症狀都只係可能，爆得輕微可以唔會有太多症狀"},{"pid":"9430cda478c5225bdba7ab5cf78595c624bddfb2","tid":326324,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb872d5008166fc71ca20bfa67b53648c871717","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好擔心"},{"pid":"7bf0111b76b6da779d9e2acb5e8a939074221015","tid":326324,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"有病根本唔洗諗睇乜專科<br />\n<br />\n睇左普通科診所先，有需要會轉介你去醫院照X光<br />\n<br />\n你做得office工應該有公司保險架照claim返"},{"pid":"de987ffc03ebca3dc54552f7722d91bd5028c7d3","tid":326324,"uid":12433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆肺可以好快，大前提係你血含氧嗰個reading要低過正常<br />\n<br />\nps如果第一次爆而且唔嚴重既醫生儘量唔會開刀的，真係要開刀都幾大件事<br />\n<br />\n利申爆過兩次"},{"pid":"14582b6116be355102a2ba5845ed8b5826008298","tid":326324,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"爆肺係唔可以深呼吸到 一吸大氣就勁痛 好似有野扯住同有針吉胸口咁<br />\n<br />\n我之前幾年都有 近兩年做多左運動無事"},{"pid":"260de2b77bde2ab9edb9dcef14c6806013734c05","tid":326324,"uid":91601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦仲問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚憎見到呢啲post，睇完醫生咪知咩事囉"},{"pid":"fece314994032fbfaf625d10e84e3d68435cee7d","tid":326324,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7094b610e8b08b6ebb293cd99e5bf173112a9d28","tid":326324,"uid":90564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"其實，你去睇醫生，之後應該會轉介去照X Ray，如果堅係爆肺，急症嚟，去急症室。<br />\n<br />\n利申：爆過三次，住咗兩個月半"},{"pid":"155fcc6e7dd01844917a9b00dbf64575fb0e7ce5","tid":326324,"uid":36146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:24:28.000Z","msg":"借朋友account覆樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你烏低小小個人向前, 如果覺得心口好似有D水流咁既感覺, 多數係爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想快既直接去睇私家, 叫佢寫信轉介你去急症室<br />\n入到去應該唔使點等就會比人推你去照X-RAY, 因為爆肺可大可小<br />\n如果照到既就睇爆左幾多%, 小既可以唔使做手術<br />\n多既就要開刀, 補/切左小小個肺, 不過而加醫學發達, 做微創傷口好細<br />\n訓1個星期醫院左右就OK<br />\n<br />\n利申睇私家+有保險CLAIM晒全數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ab22f08c6bb1e069e44433df65ee723cfa4ed6","tid":326324,"uid":13181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好擔心</blockquote><br />\n好快, 15min內睇到<br />\n利申: 爆過, 入急症睇"},{"pid":"74e4bc04e54bbe620626b289f9fb351e8d08898d","tid":326324,"uid":19267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆肺可以好快，大前提係你血含氧嗰個reading要低過正常<br />\n<br />\nps如果第一次爆而且唔嚴重既醫生儘量唔會開刀的，真係要開刀都幾大件事<br />\n<br />\n利申爆過兩次</blockquote><br />\n好似血含氧量低過正常水平都會好快 上次肺炎睇急症佢睇完血含氧量同血糖之後直接推咗張輪椅過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b071b4983457dcb3a30aa973b498a0a859c23d16","tid":326324,"uid":35229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好擔心</blockquote><br />\n好快, 15min內睇到<br />\n利申: 爆過, 入急症睇</blockquote><br />\n基本上你去到同佢講就入得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992724c4f8188c04813d1128c076aabf33032f30","tid":326324,"uid":3011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"直接去急症講懷疑爆肺 佢會好快幫你睇<br />\n錯日"},{"pid":"5a5b873e92c7eeeb5312a87b9872ccc6341a9477","tid":326324,"uid":3011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接去急症講懷疑爆肺 佢會好快幫你睇<br />\n錯日</blockquote><br />\n未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經都試過好似係咁 拖左幾日頂唔順去睇 好彩係肋骨發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a384b0f81ac04c43b5b5fd159caea33b7eb8e27","tid":326324,"uid":28328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"爆肺成因係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97054feeb54c83a0769570013854b5180aa83519","tid":326324,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆肺成因係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個肺有d液體包住，d液體少咗有個窿就係"},{"pid":"29ca277783c2549e5d77ae991b9e6d9dfd5dad9f","tid":326324,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"我都爆過幾次，去黃大仙個蔡堅睇（佢好似係有料嘢嚟），佢會即刻寫張嘢叫我去照肺。小爆肺唔會死，佢會自己好返，大件事先有機做手術。當初我發現係攤喺度突然心口勁痛，之後幾日keep住一唞氣就有痛，最後肺都冇去照就好返了"},{"pid":"f7fe7b69da608823f9edc6e05c69f591fb2dad5b","tid":326324,"uid":41643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"睇急症啦<br />\n縮得太多要插喉抽血水<br />\n利申：爆過兩次，刮埋肺"},{"pid":"f35112e6c67b9967626b131871a9d7c298785556","tid":326324,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"咁奴，做晒啲野先啦"},{"pid":"f1b9ddb065b368ff70ab019dece4d4076b757589","tid":326324,"uid":201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇急症啦<br />\n縮得太多要插喉抽血水<br />\n利申：爆過兩次，刮埋肺</blockquote><br />\n深呼吸hold住痛就去好睇啦<br />\n我上次爆,個醫生比我揀插針定插喉<br />\n我問插喉有冇痲醉,佢話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後揀插針,就咁插落去<br />\n頭2針都好好地,第3針搵個見習黎插就出事,插錯位,搞到我食多左一針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後訓4日醫院就出左院,拎左3年輕工紙,差唔多乜野重野都唔駛我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08f0c4612689746ba721c40c8424734a5e3dda2","tid":326324,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9 爆肺唔會自己好 會死 快d去睇急症<br />\n利申爆過"},{"pid":"ad8e7430007c8e1c30c473084c5265c26f3eb937","tid":326324,"uid":39886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"一定要睇急症 佢會即刻幫你插管急救，要快，如果拖耐左有機會有生命危險<br />\n利申：過來人"},{"pid":"35ff4f7e4ad9459dad4356b37963ed506d1c9d8e","tid":326324,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"依家去睇私家<br />\n多謝關心"},{"pid":"1aed451f27a90a26a009870dbd0295c917bd4f02","tid":326324,"uid":126506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"傷風感冒就去睇急症 肺都爆埋就去睇私家"},{"pid":"a84b9d89048d19100e4a568127bfaed8bd595f4f","tid":326324,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪高瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 咁辛苦去睇急症啦"},{"pid":"002f4a809f654660e44551adc7e11571baa7f2f7","tid":326324,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"冇啦啦其實點會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05cea5b45d7ddb2762d85b7d9b9ef33817f298d","tid":326324,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"803355523d1bee0dbfe77337f87498cdd31b4621","tid":326324,"uid":40397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦ON_9重上來問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為公司趕貨就唔可以休息<br />\n你死左公司係咪會賠番一千幾百萬比你家人做安家費?"},{"pid":"19bf23caee4d1aebe456f73ea472f3e586d6a6c3","tid":326324,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇啦啦其實點會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多case 都係無啦啦爆"},{"pid":"7547766490cfcaaef38f1df0a82e9053004ef4cf","tid":326324,"uid":61333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"係咪爆肺基本上入去一照x光就知 唔好拖<br />\n利申 爆過三次 第一次成個左肺冧咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n插喉又唔係話好痛既 定係可能我承受能力高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd6600f7b91c94cf9f295df7815e82226f52725","tid":326324,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"爆完一次肺之後 依家成日都無啦啦個鼻 鼻塞咁撚樣索 但又無痛咩都無 有無巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cb920b96dbc37c0effa381e6a06d80ac77b6b4","tid":326324,"uid":35229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪爆肺基本上入去一照x光就知 唔好拖<br />\n利申 爆過三次 第一次成個左肺冧咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n插喉又唔係話好痛既 定係可能我承受能力高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都爆過5次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都係插得一次喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60445201aa752a11dfcdb023adcda0231355cc54","tid":326324,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去私家照左X光先啦，係爆先去急症室。<br />\n利申 爆左成個星期先入院。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胸肺科? 耳鼻喉係咪冇用?</blockquote><br />\n屌你直接同個醫生講抖氣心口好痛，叫佢俾你照肺，照完醫生同你睇左你真係爆就直接打999叫白車啦。<br />\n屌你老母寧願上網問都唔直接死去睇醫生。"},{"pid":"c57a441efbf318f866de2605df3ec9ec910944ed","tid":326324,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d6fa472c425d31861615f168923dc0ccfe4677e","tid":326324,"uid":18649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:14:35.000Z","msg":"身體出問題仲可以掛住公事<br />\n<br />\n叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d482bfd075b99d29685e576737863282ec44d56e","tid":326324,"uid":108968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:24:34.000Z","msg":"下次炒車係咪都要上嚟問左先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af627dde3facb1fc3872e2f14ca36278429e165","tid":326324,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79e046f0f7f19d794da05283878c86bcc6bd948d","tid":326324,"uid":116616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"[quote]我索鼻索咗好耐, 初頭應該係妥瑞症返發<br />\n但近一個月, 好似唞唔到氣咁, 要係咁狂索(索到有聲)先至稍為停一陣<br />\n呢個星期仲要索鼻嗰時右邊背脊痛+右心口痛+右膊頭痛, 轉身/ 瞓低/ 打乞次都痛<br />\n<br />\n我以為係扭傷, 但今日突然諗到會唔會係爆肺<br />\n求問, 會唔會係爆肺, 要睇咩專科醫生, 仲有可唔可以唔打針/手術?<br />\n事關我怕痛, 加上公司趕緊貨, 好難唞7-9日<br />\n<br />\n老母同我book咗星期六耳鼻喉專科, 同佢講個肺係咪都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係唔理佢, 星期六睇其他?<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n求各位巴絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote］<br />\n<br />\n睇你有referred pain 上背脊同頸部，嗰個位係肺既referred pain site，樓主都係速速睇急症啦，d symptoms 好有可能係pneumothorax"},{"pid":"5c700d3aebed7110c0e7a85e591ffc0f5747e2b2","tid":326324,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:03:24.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f67975cbda01c3a46ab583ac9799d302f62179","tid":326324,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆完一次肺之後 依家成日都無啦啦個鼻 鼻塞咁撚樣索 但又無痛咩都無 有無巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有鼻塞"},{"pid":"d42885e3bd518c298a593871b778c2648ced86ac","tid":326324,"uid":17319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"好大機會係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快手唔好拖 會死人架"},{"pid":"9b74c3b0403d8ccb5cf7535e4956615126b24f07","tid":326324,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"疑似爆肺去急症照張x光望望啦."},{"pid":"1b2094ac2a6ce9ac374f3220561f97461d079664","tid":326324,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急症唔知要排幾耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都要排架啦..."}]}